Class MappedBytes

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.openhft.chronicle.bytes.AbstractBytes<Void>
      • net.openhft.chronicle.bytes.MappedBytes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, Appendable, AutoCloseable, CharSequence, Bytes<Void>, BytesComment<BytesOut<Void>>, BytesIn<Void>, BytesOut<Void>, BytesPrepender<Bytes<Void>>, BytesStore<Bytes<Void>,Void>, ByteStringAppender<Bytes<Void>>, RandomDataInput, RandomDataOutput<Bytes<Void>>, StreamingCommon<Bytes<Void>>, StreamingDataInput<Bytes<Void>>, StreamingDataOutput<Bytes<Void>>, net.openhft.chronicle.core.ReferenceCounted

    public class MappedBytes
extends AbstractBytes<Void>
implements net.openhft.chronicle.core.io.Closeable
    Bytes to wrap memory mapped data.

    NOTE These Bytes are single Threaded as are all Bytes.
